ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of PAULE ROBITAILLE of Montréal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of eight months or a period expiring on the day prior to the coming into force of the Balance Refugee Reform Act, whichever period ends earlier, effective March 26, 2012.
